error`\n48:     - `List(ctx, filter) ([]*Session, error)`\n49:   - Define `SessionFilter` struct for list filtering\n50:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n51: \n52: ### Phase 3: Error Types (Optional)\n53: \n54: - [ ] **T3.1** Define custom error types in `pkg/store/errors.go`\n55:   - `SessionNotFoundError`\n56:   - `SessionAlreadyExistsError`\n57:   - `SessionStoreError`\n58:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n59: \n60: ### Phase 4: Unit Tests\n61: \n62: - [ ] **T4.1** Create `pkg/store/session_test.go`\n63:   - Test Session struct JSON serialization/deserialization\n64:   - Test SessionFilter with various filter combinations\n65:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v`\n66: \n67: ### Phase 5: Validation & Quality\n68: \n69: - [ ] **T5.1** Run `go vet ./pkg/store/...`\n70:   - Fix any issues reported\n71: \n72: - [ ] **T5.2** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/store/...`\n73:   - Fix any linting issues\n74: \n75: - [ ] **T5.3** Verify JSON tags use camelCase\n76:   - Check: `sandboxId`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt`, `expiresAt`, `lastActiveAt`\n77: \n78: ---\n79: \n80: ## Task Dependencies\n81: \n82: ```\n83: T1.1 → T1.2 → T2.1 → T2.2 → T2.3 → T3.1 → T4.1 → T5.1 → T5.2 → T5.3\n84: ```\n85: \n86: ---\n87: \n88: ## Verification Commands\n89: \n90: | Task | Verification Command |\n91: |------|----------------------|\n92: | T1.2 | `go mod tidy && go mod verify` |\n93: | T2.1-T2.3 | `go build ./pkg/store/...` |\n94: | T3.1 | `go build ./pkg/store/...` |\n95: | T4.1 | `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -cover` |\n96: | T5.1 | `go vet ./pkg/store/...` |\n97: | T5.2 | `golangci-lint run ./pkg/store/...` |\n98: \n99: ---\n100: \n101: ## Acceptance Criteria\n102: \n103: - [ ] SessionStore 接口定义完整\n104: - [ ] Session 数据结构包含必要字段\n105: - [ ] SessionFilter 支持基本过滤\n106: - [ ] Pass `go vet` with zero issues\n107: - [ ] Pass `golangci-lint` with zero issues\n108: - [ ] JSON tags 使用 camelCase\n109: - [ ] Unit tests pass\n110: \n111: ---\n112: \n113: ## Notes\n114: \n115: - 仅定义接口，不实现具体存储逻辑\n116: - 具体实现由后续 AR 提供 (如 Redis 实现)\n117: - 接口设计参考 Session Manager 使用场景\n118: \n119: ---\n120: \n121: ## Implementation Timeline\n122: \n123: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n124: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n125: | Phase 1: Project Setup | T1.1-T1.2 | Not Started | 0% |\n126: | Phase 2: Core Type Definitions | T2.1-T2.3 | Not Started | 0% |\n127: | Phase 3: Error Types | T3.1 | Not Started | 0% |\n128: | Phase 4: Unit Tests | T4.1 | Not Started | 0% |\n129: | Phase 5: Validation | T5.1-T5.3 | Not Started | 0% |\n130: \n131: **Total Progress: 0% Complete**\n\n(End of file - total 131 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-0] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Project Setup\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Create directory structure `pkg/store/`\n- [ ] **T1.2** Verify Go module exists and add dependencies if needed","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775856853038,"end":1775856853065}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775856853068,"sessionID":"ses_286af0d57ffeW3HL0YEIOacn4B","part":{"id":"prt_d79511b43001iTKafVbZ81b7ko","messageID":"msg_d795107e3001F2zvDI7g1nLNtz","sessionID":"ses_286af0d57ffeW3HL0YEIOacn4B","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-3963a3be41924afba07d1c832b6fa5ff","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/store` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-0 |\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: 定义会话存储的抽象接口和数据结构，包括:\n16: - `SessionStore` 接口定义\n17: - `Session` 数据结构\n18: - 存储操作方法签名\n19: \n20: ## Out of Scope\n21: \n22: - 具体存储实现 (Redis、Memory 等)\n23: - 存储连接池管理\n24: - 分布式锁实现\n25: \n26: ## Dependencies\n27: \n28: 无外部依赖。\n29: \n30: ## Deliverables\n31: \n32: | File | Description |\n33: |------|-------------|\n34: | `pkg/store/store.go` | SessionStore 接口定义 |\n35: | `pkg/store/session.go` | Session 数据结构 |\n36: | `pkg/store/doc.go` | 包文档 |\n37: \n38: ## Acceptance Criteria\n39: \n40: - [ ] 接口定义完整\n41: - [ ] Session 数据结构包含必要字段\n42: - [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n43: \n44: ## References\n45: \n46: - 待补充\n\n(End of file - total 46 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义会话存储的抽象接口和数据结构，包括:\n- `SessionStore` 接口定义\n- `Session` 数据结构\n- 存储操作方法签名\n\n## Out of Scope","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/spec.md","t